00F0B6  2               ; perform COPPER subcommand — full handler relocated to extension ROM.
00F0B6  2               ; Saves ~390 bytes in BASIC ROM. EXT_COPPER in extension.s parses raw
00F0B6  2               ; BASIC text via (Bpntrl),Y and uses RAM bridges (EXT_GTBY, EXT_GTWRD,
00F0B6  2               ; EXT_SNERR) to reach BASIC's numeric expression evaluator and syntax
00F0B6  2               ; error path.
00F0B6  2               
00F0B6  2               LAB_COPPER
00F0B6  2  A9 0C              LDA   #EXT_CMD_COPPER
00F0B8  2  4C 21 02           JMP   EXT_vec
